# SUBOFF Cursor Rules

- At the start of every new chat in this workspace, read `EXPERIENCE.md` in this
  directory before making plans or editing files.
- Only modify files under `d:\OpenFOAM\v2312\SUBOFF`.
  Do not edit parent repository files, sibling project folders, global Cursor
  settings, or files outside this directory unless the user explicitly approves
  that exact path.
- Preserve existing user changes. Do not run destructive cleanup, reset, or
  checkout commands unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer local project conventions over generic advice. This project mixes
  OpenFOAM v2312 case files, MATLAB and FORTRAN pre/post-processing scripts,
  and shell run scripts.
- When changing mesh dimensions, point ordering, boundary data, decomposition,
  or generated OpenFOAM files, update the relevant README or `EXPERIENCE.md`
  notes so the workflow remains reproducible.
- Keep generated/check files conceptually separate from source scripts and
  downstream OpenFOAM inputs. Document which files are for Tecplot inspection
  and which are copied or consumed by later case steps.
